The dataset is structured hierarchically to classify emotional states (Angry, Sad, Happy, Normal) based on signature variations. 
Each individual has a unique folder containing subfolders for different emotions, with multiple signature samples under each category. 

FLOW CHART REPRESENTATION
📁 Dataset
│
├── 📂 Person1
│   ├── 📂 Angry → [signature1.png, signature2.png, ...]
│   ├── 📂 Sad → [signature1.png, signature2.png, ...]
│   ├── 📂 Happy → [signature1.png, signature2.png, ...]
│   ├── 📂 Normal → [signature1.png, signature2.png, ...]
│
├── 📂 Person2
│   ├── 📂 Angry → [signature1.png, signature2.png, ...]
│   ├── 📂 Sad → [signature1.png, signature2.png, ...]
│   ├── 📂 Happy → [signature1.png, signature2.png, ...]
│   ├── 📂 Normal → [signature1.png, signature2.png, ...]
│
└── (More individuals follow the same structure)
